{
  "stem": "19837.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 72.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the truth was they wanted us for customers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a Sabbath, where my father-in-law and my sister-in-law didn't ride.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they walked next to my rickshaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I had the baby, I was allowed to take the rickshaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My in-laws had rented us one room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother-in-law was always very cheerful and encouraging.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, we're all here together, and we have nothing to complain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We hope that my parents and her youngest son, they will make it, plus all the rest of the people they want to come.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we have nothing to complain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Selma Sinasohn.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was born named Sinasohn, her maiden name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same as the uncle in Paris, S-I-N-A-S-O-H-N.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One room.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No toilet, no kitchen, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We washed clothes in cold water, hung it on the bamboo sticks, I think it's called, that goes from one window to another across a lane.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The lane was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the lane had a lot of little houses, so to say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And downstairs, everybody washed in cold water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And like I say, we hung it on the bamboo sticks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the wintertime, it got so stiff that you couldn't even use it when it was dry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't to begin with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't later, either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got help from-- well, the names were all different, the organizations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Red Cross came in there, too, in the war, during the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we, we had to-- we had big camps where my husband and I, or my family-- the others also didn't go-- only the first night we had to go there to register, so to say, to be eligible for the food.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so then we all went every day with a little pot and picked up the food.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
